---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="没有找到这条路" description="页面不存在，回到去你想去的地方继续阅读。">
  <main class="shell page-shell not-found-page">
    <section class="page-hero not-found-hero">
      <span class="eyebrow">404</span>
      <h1>这条路暂时走不通</h1>
      <p>可能是链接写错了，也可能这篇文章还在路上。先回到文章列表，或者按 AI 入门路线继续读。</p>
      <div class="not-found-actions">
        <a class="button secondary" href="/posts/">查看文章</a>
        <a class="button secondary" href="/ai-roadmap/">AI 入门路线</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
